event AssetAdded(address indexed market, address indexed collateralAsset, bytes4 pluginSelector)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
event PluginAdded(address indexed plugin, bytes4 pluginSelector)
function addAsset(address market, address collateralAsset, address flp, bytes4 pluginSelector, uint256 leverage)
function assets(address, address) view returns (uint256 leverage, address flp, bytes4 pluginSelector)
function executeMultiplier(address market, address collateralAsset, uint256 initialAmount, uint256 leverageBps, bytes swapData, uint256 minAmountOut)
function plugins(bytes4) view returns (address endpoint, bytes config)
